  "detailed_description": "Blazing Crow is a SLG-based puzzle game(PUZ). In game,you will play As A Crow to Defeat Human!<br>Crows are tiny, but smart. Try to figure out human behavior patterns, let themattack themselves!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966190/extras/ec0106e0f1273dd7b0ab1959ab797281.poster.avif?t=1723901580\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966190/extras/ec0106e0f1273dd7b0ab1959ab797281.webm?t=1723901580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>From a certain point in time, non-stop snowstorms cut humans into small settlements. Enslaved, domesticated, they tried to find a way out of the crows.<br>Is there still fire in this frozen world?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966190/extras/ffb1d0ccd4d68fd66e571750ab1f1324.avif?t=1723901580\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br>Save the crows, even if everything is irretrievably lost...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966190/extras/281654314e4f0cbff248313dfcfb6d18.avif?t=1723901580\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
